<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.2">
<l>pōrkaḷi ṟuporu māliruñ cōlaiyam pūmpuṟavil</l>
<l>tārkkoṭi mullaika ḷuntava ḷanakai kāṭṭukiṉṟa</l>
<l>kārkkoḷ paṭākkaḷniṉ ṟukaḻa ṟiccirik kattariyē</l>
<l>ṉārkkiṭu kōtōḻī yavaṉṟār ceyta pūcalaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even the jasmines from creepers with buds in the lovely, flowering forests of</l>
<l>Māliruñcōlai, where belligerent elephants fight, show [His] white teeth.</l>
<l>As the fresh bedaly emetic nut [creepers] constantly say [that I cannot escape] and laugh,</l>
<l rend="indent">I shall not bear [it].</l>
<l>To whom shall [I] complain, O friend! about the distress caused by His garland?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
